summary: This document is a subpoena issued to MoneyGram International, Inc. requesting all available financial transaction records related to Ghislaine Maxwell. It seeks detailed information on money transfers and money order purchases using Maxwell's identifiers, indicating a financial investigation into her activities.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The subpoena requests all financial transaction records (money transfers, money orders) associated with her identifiers (name, DOB, SSN, addresses, phone, email) from inception through the present date.

locations: MoneyGram International, Inc., 1550 Utica Avenue South MS: MBC-5508, Minneapolis, MN 55416
keyFacts: A subpoena was issued to MoneyGram International for all financial records related to Ghislaine Maxwell.
The request seeks comprehensive transaction data including sender/payee details, purchase locations, amounts, dates, and forms of payment.
The investigation period covers from the inception of records through the present, indicating a broad financial audit.
Maxwell's listed identifiers include addresses in Boston, MA and New York, NY, suggesting multiple locations of interest.
